Destructor sat up with a shot. "Hydras I think we  have a problem. I see 
Cyngar Tyrael and Maximal forces confergeing on one spot." Hydras turned with 
a sharp look. "This can not bold well. I would be a fool to not see an attack 
coming form this. All troops come to the bridge waspinator quickstrike proto 
nightshade all of you come here now." He then turned to the new recruits. 
"Well this will be interesting."
